                    <h3>SSL Connections</h3>
					<p>App Service supports two types of SSL connections: Server Name Indication (SNI) SSL connections and IP address SSL connections. SNI-based SSL is suitable for modern browsers while IP-based SSL is suitable for all browsers.</p>
                    <p>There is no charge for using SNI-based SSL. One IP SSL can be used with the Standard and Premium service plans at no additional charge. The Free and Shared service plans do not support SSL. You can purchase the right to use more SSL connections at the prices below. In all cases, the SSL certificate itself must be purchased separately.</p>
